name: PlayStation Underground: Jampack Winter 2001
synopsis: A collection of demos from the Official PlayStation Magazine. The disc contains demos of [[Baldur's Gate: Dark Alliance]], [[Drakan: The Ancients' Gates]], [[Extermination]], [[Final Fantasy X]], [[Kinetica]], [[SSX Tricky]], videos of [[Dynasty Warriors 3]], [[Jak and Daxter: The Precursor Legacy]], [[Okage: Shadow King]], [[Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 3]] as well as Behind-the-Scenes movies on Jak and Daxter: The Precursors Legacy and Extermination.
